IRREGULAR VERBS                                                                         prepared by Uğur ARSLAN, @arslanuguur

V1              V2                  V3
Present         Past                Perfect
Infinitive      Simple Past         Past participle         Turkish                                       Examples/Extras
                                    Adjective
